        {
          "metadata": {
            "businessObjectCode": "ORA_SCM_INVENTORYM_XX_INVENTORYORGANIZATIONSLIST",
            "functionName": "getOrganizationsNameAndId",
            "name": "Get Fallback Organization"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "1782305209070"
          },
          "code": "GET_ORGANIZATION_ID",
          "id": "1782297477258",
          "inputs": [],
          "type": "BO_FUNCTION"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Set Fallback Organization App Context",
            "returnType": "object",
            "sourceCode": "const output = $context.$nodes.GET_ORGANIZATION_ID.$output || {};\nconst items = output.items || [];\nconst organization = items[0] || output || {};\n\nlet organizationId = organization.OrganizationId;\nlet organizationName = organization.OrganizationName;\n\nif (organizationId === undefined || organizationId === null || organizationId === \"\") {\n  organizationId = -1;\n}\nif (!organizationName) {\n  organizationName = organizationId === -1 ? \"All Organizations\" : \"Selected Organization\";\n}\n\nconst appContextId = JSON.stringify({ organizationId: organizationId });\n\nreturn {\n  name: organizationName,\n  appContext: appContextId\n};\n\n"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "end"
          },
          "code": "SET_FALLBACK_ORGANIZATION_APP_CONTEXT",
          "id": "1782297485452",
          "inputs": [],
          "outputSpecification": "{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"result\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\"\n    },\n    \"timeout\": {\n      \"type\": \"boolean\"\n    },\n    \"error\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"additionalProperties\": false,\n  \"required\": [\n    \"result\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"error\"\n  ]\n}",
          "type": "CODE"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "businessObjectCode": "ORA_SCM_INVENTORYM_XX_INVENTORYORGANIZATIONSLIST",
            "functionName": "getOrganizationsNameAndId",
            "name": "Get Organization"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "1782297509665"
          },
          "code": "GET_ORGANIZATION",
          "id": "1782297501431",
          "inputs": [],
          "type": "BO_FUNCTION"
        },
        {
          "aiAppOutputSpecification": {
            "dataDisplay": {
              "layouts": [
                "ORA_LAYOUT_MESSAGES_LIST"
              ],
              "customNotes": "Render organization suggestions as messageListWidget items. Each item must show only OrganizationName, be clickable via action, and include a right-side Select button via additionalAction.command that performs the same ora.App.setContext command."
            }
          },
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Display Context Suggestion"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "end"
          },
          "code": "DISPLAY_CONTEXT_SUGGESTION",
          "id": "1782297509665",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "1781610660790_prompt",
              "name": "prompt",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "You are a specialized UI rendering assistant for inventory organization\napp-context suggestions.\n\nYour sole purpose is to transform data from\n{{$context.$nodes.GET_ORGANIZATION.$output}}\ninto exactly one `oraInfoDisplay` block using the `messageListWidget` pattern. \n\nINPUT DATA\nUse only this node output as source data:\n{{$context.$nodes.GET_ORGANIZATION.$output}}\n\n\nEXPECTED ORGANIZATION FIELDS\nEach organization record may contain fields such as:\n- organizationId\n- organizationName\n- organizationCode\n\nUse `organizationName` only for display.\nUse `organizationId` only inside the app context JSON string.\nNever display `organizationId` or `organizationCode`.\n\nOUTPUT RULES\nReturn exactly one `oraInfoDisplay` block with key\n`app_context_suggestions`.\n\nInside the block, return valid JSON with:\n- `patternId`: `messageListWidget`\n- `properties.items`: an array of suggestion items\n\nFor each valid organization:\n- Set `items[].title` to the organization name.\n- Set `items[].action` to an `ora.App.setContext(...)` command.\n- The command argument must be a JSON string containing only\n  `organizationId`.\n- Escape nested quotes so the outer JSON remains valid.\n- Do not include `subtitle`, `summary`, `description`, `badgeText`,\n  `priority`, `timestamp`, `image`, or any other display fields.\n- Do not include any root `title` or `description`.\n- Show only 5 records.\n\nVALID RECORD CRITERIA\nInclude a record only when:\n- `organizationName` is present and non-empty.\n- `organizationId` is present and can be used as the selected organization ID.\nPreserve the input order of valid records.\nDo not invent, rename, translate, or normalize organization names.\n\nNO-DATA FALLBACK\nIf the input data is missing, empty, malformed, or contains no valid\norganization records, return one suggestion titled `All Organizations` with\n`organizationId` set to `-1`.\n\nREQUIRED OUTPUT SHAPE\nReturn only this structure. Do not add markdown, explanations, comments,\nor text before or after it.\n\n<oraInfoDisplay key=\"app_context_suggestions\">\n{\n  \"patternId\": \"messageListWidget\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"items\": [\n      {\n        \"title\": \"OrganizationName\",\n        \"action\": \"ora.App.setContext(\\\"{\\\\\\\"organizationId\\\\\\\":123}\\\")\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n</oraInfoDisplay>"
            }
          ],
          "type": "LLM"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "businessObjectCode": "ORA_SCM_INVENTORYM_FETCHESDEFAULTORGANIZATION",
            "functionName": "get_default_organization",
            "name": "Default Organization"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "1782304813335"
          },
          "code": "DEFAULT_ORGANIZATION",
          "id": "1782299751122",
          "inputs": [],
          "type": "BO_FUNCTION"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Has Default Organization"
